  "blurb": "A contemporary two-bedroom penthouse of around 311 m² across two floors in the gated Laguna resort lands at Bang Tao, Phuket, looking out over the lagoon and the sea. Modern interiors threaded with traditional Thai detail, a full kitchen and a private balcony — minutes from Bang Tao Beach, Boat Avenue and the golf course.",
  "detail": "Set high in a contemporary residence within the Laguna resort enclave at Bang Tao, this two-bedroom penthouse spreads across roughly 311 square metres across two floors and frames wide views over the lagoon and the Andaman beyond. Its design blends a modern, light-filled sensibility with traditional Thai detail, drawn from the culture of the island.\n\nThe living and dining spaces are open and airy, opening to a private balcony for sunset drinks, with a fully-equipped kitchen for easy in-residence meals. Two bedrooms with quality linens and en-suite bathrooms — one with a bathtub — make it an easy base for a family or two couples.\n\nThe setting is one of Phuket’s most connected: about 1.4 km to Bang Tao Beach, 2 km to the restaurants and boutiques of Boat Avenue, and roughly 3 km to the Laguna golf course, the Cherngtalay temple and the Blue Tree water park. Air-conditioning, ceiling fans, elevator access, a BBQ grill, beach essentials and an in-app concierge round out a comfortable, serviced stay.",
